# OpenClaw Routing Intent

When generating or updating app deployment manifests:

1. Enforce Traefik label-based routing.
2. Prefer zero host port exposure and route through Traefik.
3. Preserve wildcard subdomain flow for Cloudflare Access.
4. Ask for missing app internal port if not provided.
5. Fail closed on insecure defaults (no HTTP-only public routing unless explicitly requested).
